Rating: 2
I made this bread to compliment "Chicken Salad With Grapes and Walnuts" (on this site). The bread was good (and the salad was EXCELLENT), but I don't think that this bread recipe should claim to have perfect proportions of everything. I used 1/2 of a loaf of Italian bread to make 8 slices, so I divided everything in 1/2. The amount of garlic butter was a bit scant to put on each side of each slice. Next time I would only butter one side of each slice, so that the butter was thick on one side, while the other side of the same slice of bread was relatively non-greasy. Then I think that the garlic butter flavor would be stronger and better.

